Welcome to PipeLab ProcessPlanner Documentation!

The PipeLab Module consists of several submodules and classes. It uses type aliases for easier comprehension of complex types, which can be found in type dictionary. The most important modules are the OPC-UA server and the GUI for debugging and visualization.
